  <?dbhtml filename="icon-naming-utils.html"?>

  <title>icon-naming-utils-&icon-naming-utils-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The icon-naming-utils package contains a Perl script used for maintaining
      backwards compatibility with current desktop icon themes, while migrating
      to the names specified in the <ulink
      url="http://standards.freedesktop.org/icon-naming-spec/latest/"> Icon
      Naming Specification</ulink>.
    </para>

